{"tid":1325964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府資訊科技總監： 會向市民解說「多功能智慧燈柱」","createTime":"2019-07-17T05:04:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T08:07:55.000Z","uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"62f79976e3e9ed62ab5020f880d53cb2127c9abc","tid":1325964,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:04:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190717/_2019071710595468111.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190717%2F_2019071710595468111.jpg&h=c41f2b24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府於各區開始分階段增設智慧燈柱，不過有市民對此有私隱疑慮，政府回應指，<strong>3項監測功能暫時不會啟用</strong>。助理政府資訊科技總監黃志光表示，會盡快公開每支智慧燈柱的位置、設備及功能等資料，供公眾監察應用，以釋疑慮。<br />\n<br />\n黃志光冀最快在一個月內，成立由10名業內專家組成的諮詢委員會，將評估目前智慧燈柱是否符合私隱指引等。他說，在獲委員會滿意安排及確保技術可應用，會到區議會諮詢，並<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">向市民解釋，再決定安裝時間表</span></strong>。"},{"pid":"dbaad4a7a9977f092f6d9e159c4e26c084da9ca5","tid":1325964,"uid":260367,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:05:10.000Z","msg":"好多監控功能嘅燈柱"},{"pid":"81d660243993c6d6e81c0e041740035b6dc68cd8","tid":1325964,"uid":125168,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:05:48.000Z","msg":"林鄭d論調<br />\n市民反對，只會換黎解釋<br />\n無普選真係唔得掂"},{"pid":"5264d3615f31cad2503cc9b249e190f157bcf7f9","tid":1325964,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:05:58.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1546281/即時-港聞-將公開各智慧燈柱位置及功能-黃志光-會諮詢區議會及向市民解釋\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1546281%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E5%B0%87%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E5%90%84%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7%E7%87%88%E6%9F%B1%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%8F%8A%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD-%E9%BB%83%E5%BF%97%E5%85%89-%E6%9C%83%E8%AB%AE%E8%A9%A2%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E5%8F%8A%E5%90%91%E5%B8%82